# Local Content Staging
# distribution/ is tracked intentionally — it holds public-facing project
# strategy (AI discovery, competitor landscape, package registry, publishing
# queue, content tracker, etc.) that benefits viewers and contributors.
# Personal/career-sensitive files inside it stay local-only:
distribution/EMPLOYER_SIGNAL.md
distribution/EXPOSURE_AUDIT_LOG.md
distribution/EXPOSURE_IMPACT_REVIEW.md
